data.description: Absolutely Stunning Home In La Privada at Verde Santa Fe. Backing to the Agave Highlands Golf Course with Spectacular Views! Gated Courtyard Entry leads you into the popular Sienna floor plan that features 2 bedrooms plus den/office with private full bath (that could easily be converted to a 3rd bedroom) & a separate great room & family room w/ gas fireplace. Remodeled Kitchen includes gorgeous knotty Alder cabinets, gas range with double oven & electric wall oven, granite counter tops, custom backsplash, breakfast bar, walk in pantry & dining area adjacent to the family room. Large Master Suite w/ walk in closet & a beautifully remodeled ensuite. Step out back on to the covered back patio w/ amazing views. So many upgrades & improvements, please ask for the list. This home is a must see!
